---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import logoImage from '../../assets/logo.png';
---

<Layout title="About Alvin Tolentino">
  <main class="bg-white">
    <section class="pt-40 pb-24 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-boho-navy mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest">Alvin Tolentino</h1>
        <p class="text-2xl text-boho-gold font-barlow tracking-widest uppercase mb-12 border-b border-boho-wheat pb-6">
          Systems Architect & Engineering Leader
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-lg text-boho-navy/80 font-sans leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Alvin Tolentino is a technology leader focused on operational stability and systems clarity. With over 20 years of experience, Alvin specializes in the intersection where complex code meets human motivation.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Alvin’s journey through international relocations, managing support communities, and navigating professional turnarounds has shaped a deeply human-centric worldview. He approaches technical and organizational challenges with the belief that long-term success is built on empathy, clear communication, and high ethical standards.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-boho-wheat/10 p-8 my-10 border-l-4 border-boho-gold">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-boho-navy mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">Navigating High-Conflict Environments</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-boho-navy/80">
              Having managed chaotic tech environments and challenging personal chapters, Alvin understands the complexities of working in high-friction spaces. He uses his experience in systems architecture and martial arts discipline to help teams bridge communication gaps. He focuses on transforming fragmented teams into collaborative, stable, and highly functional units.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p>
            Today, as the co-founder of Star and Stream, Alvin is dedicated to teaching others how to achieve professional success with integrity. He builds systems and mentors individuals to handle the volatility of the modern workforce.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
